{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.time()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/time","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/debug\"><code>debug()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/error\"><code>error()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/info\"><code>info()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Console API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Non-standard:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Inicia um cronômetro que você pode usar para monitorar quanto tempo uma operação leva. Você dá para cada&nbsp;cronômetro um nome único, e deve ter no máximo 10.000 deles sendo executados&nbsp;na página. Quando você chama&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>console.timeEnd()</code></a> com o mesmo nome, o navegador mostrará o tempo, em milisegundos, que se passou desde que o&nbsp;cronômetro iniciou.</p>\n\n<p>Veja <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/DOM/console#timers\">Timers&nbsp;</a>na documentação&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a> para detalhes e exemplos.</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.time(<em>label</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"label\"><code>label</code></dt>\n <dd>O nome para dar ao novo&nbsp;cronômetro. Ele identificará o&nbsp;cronômetro; use o mesmo quando chamar <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>console.timeEnd()</code></a>&nbsp;para parar o&nbsp;cronômetro e obter o tempo na saída do console.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<p><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\">API do objeto Console</a></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td>2</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/10\" title=\"Released on 2012-01-31.\">10.0</a> (10.0)</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Disponível em Workers</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/38\" title=\"Released on 2015-05-19.\">38.0</a> (38.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>10.0 (10.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Disponível em Workers</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>38.0 (38.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>Console.timeEnd()</code></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/dragonfly/documentation/console/\" rel=\" noopener\">Opera Dragonfly documentation: Console</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"summary"},{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Parâmetros","id":"parâmetros"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"Inicia um cronômetro que você pode usar para monitorar quanto tempo uma operação leva. Você dá para cada cronômetro um nome único, e deve ter no máximo 10.000 deles sendo executados na página. Quando você chama console.timeEnd() com o mesmo nome, o navegador mostrará o tempo, em milisegundos, que se passou desde que o cronômetro iniciou.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Console.time()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"console.time()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Console.time()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"console.time","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"console.time()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"console.time()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Console.time()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"console.time","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/console/time","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/console/time/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console","title":"Console"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/time","title":"Console.time()"}],"pageTitle":"Console.time() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}